《'''奶牛陰謀: 永遠不能說的秘密'''》（{{lang|en|Cowspiracy: The Sustainability Secret}}），又譯為《'''畜牧業的陰謀'''》，是由吉普·安德森及基岡·庫恩於2014年所製作的一部紀錄影片</span></span> 。影片在探討養殖畜牧業對環境的衝擊，以及調查各個[[環保組織|環保組織]]對此衝擊的應對策略。 影片中接受調查的環保組織包括，[[綠色和平|綠色和平]]、[[塞拉俱乐部|賽拉俱樂部]]，衝浪者基金會、雨林行動網路等。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/ellen-kanner/meatless-monday-cowspirac_b_5634983.html|title=Meatless Monday -- 'Cowspiracy:' The One Thing No One Talks About|accessdate=October 9, 2014|date=August 4, 2014|last=Kanner|first=Ellen|publisher=Huffington Post|archive-date=2017-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170315164809/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/ellen-kanner/meatless-monday-cowspirac_b_5634983.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://therealnews.com/t2/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=31&Itemid=74&jumival=12659 |title=Animal Agriculture: A Neglected Agent of Global Warming? |accessdate=2017-03-17 |archive-date=2017-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170223044906/http://therealnews.com/t2/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=31&Itemid=74&jumival=12659 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.villagemagazine.ie/index.php/2015/02/cowspiracy/|title=Cowspiracy|date=February 19, 2015|work=Village|authorlink=Frank Armstrong|accessdate=2015-03-04|archive-date=2015-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150224020700/http://www.villagemagazine.ie/index.php/2015/02/cowspiracy/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.sfweekly.com/foodie/2014/06/25/burgers-are-ending-the-world-says-cowspiracy|title=Burgers Are Ending the World, Says ''Cowspiracy''|date=Jun 25, 2014|work=SF Weekly|authorlink=Tiffany Do|accessdate=2015-03-04|archive-date=2015-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150311102333/http://www.sfweekly.com/foodie/2014/06/25/burgers-are-ending-the-world-says-cowspiracy|dead-url=no}}</ref>

此紀錄片是透過群眾募資網站IndieGoGo獲得贊助，由1,449 位贊助者集資籌得117,092美元。籌得金額是當初製作團隊籌款目標的217%，也因此該紀錄片有多餘的資金可以錄製西班牙語和德語的配音，還能翻成 10種以上的語言字幕，包括[[中文|中文]]和[[俄文|俄文]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/cowspiracy-the-sustainability-secret|title=Cowspiracy IndieGoGo campaign page|accessdate=2017-03-17|archive-date=2016-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161010114110/https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/cowspiracy-the-sustainability-secret|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://newint.org/blog/2015/09/24/cowspiracy-documentary-vegan/|title=Beware Cowspiracy – and the spread of the vegan virus -- New Internationalist|author=Alison Homewood|work=New Internationalist|accessdate=2017-03-17|archive-date=2017-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170321221107/https://newint.org/blog/2015/09/24/cowspiracy-documentary-vegan/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 該影片的放映是透過授權電影發行人以及Tugg網路電影院去播放。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tugg.com/titles/cowspiracy|title=Cowspiracy page on Tugg|accessdate=2017-03-17|archive-date=2017-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220121602/https://www.tugg.com/titles/cowspiracy|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

之後，同一部紀錄片有再經過重新剪輯，並由[[好萊塢|好萊塢]]影視巨星[[莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥|李奧納多·狄卡皮歐]]監製，於2015年9月15日在[[Netflix|網飛]]全球同步首映。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://decider.com/2015/08/27/cowspiracy-the-sustainability-documentary-netflix/|title=Exclusive: Interview With Directors Of ‘Cowspiracy: The Sustainability Secret’ On Netflix, A Controversial New Documentary|date=August 27, 2015|work=Decider|authorlink=Olivia Armstrong|accessdate=2015-08-28|archive-date=2015-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150828131745/http://decider.com/2015/08/27/cowspiracy-the-sustainability-documentary-netflix/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

